weavec2 — Weave Surface-Language Compiler (self-hosted)
Copyright 2026 Jukka Aho

This product includes software developed as the surface-Weave
compiler for the Weave programming language. It is itself written
in surface Weave: the source under `src/**/*.weave` is lowered to
WIR by `weavefront`, compiled to LLVM IR by `weavec1`, and linked
with `weavec0`'s runtime — the same pipeline a stranger uses to
build their own surface-Weave program through this chain.

Upstream:    https://github.com/ahojukka5/weavec2
